span.style: font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px;

p.span: Hampton School District is SAU 90, a public school system educating the students in the Town of Hampton, NH from preschool to grade 8.

span.style: font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px;
font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px;

p.span: The mission of the Hampton School District is to provide an encouraging, educational environment where the unique talents and abilities of individual students are recognized and where the learning experience is meaningful and every student achieves mastery through a firm foundation in core fundamentals, higher level of thinking, problem-solving and critical/creative communication skills.
